description: Mobstah Lobstah was created to bring the best the state of Maine and its cold Atlantic waters has to offer to hungry Floridian foodies. Presenting fresh, sustainable,  and scrumptious certified Maine lobster, shrimp, and crab rolls is this truck's passion, and fresh lobster bisque and New England clam chowder complement the delicious rolls. Check them out on the Hollywood streets today!
name: Mobstah Lobstah
